  "1902970": {
    "name": "Castle Come",
    "steam_appid": 1902970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Castle Come是一款移动堡垒roguelike游戏。在一片强盗猖獗的怪异土地上，搜索新的部件，摧毁敌人的堡垒并清理残骸，招募人员来操纵你不断充盈的武器库，从灵活的小堡垒发展到杀伤力极强的、庞大的怪物机器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/5ccfd3cb24bb83091b3f88c4d655635a.poster.avif?t=1768382106\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/5ccfd3cb24bb83091b3f88c4d655635a.webm?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/5ccfd3cb24bb83091b3f88c4d655635a.mp4?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造堡垒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买和搜寻新武器、模组和塔楼，从灵活的小堡垒发展到杀伤力极强的、庞大的怪物。  轻松拖放机枪炮塔、掷雷器、修改器、牵引光束、鸡舍、喷火器、巨石等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/154f127f667237e7d17bd1cc0ee8d5a1.poster.avif?t=1768382106\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/154f127f667237e7d17bd1cc0ee8d5a1.webm?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/154f127f667237e7d17bd1cc0ee8d5a1.mp4?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与敌人战斗，夺取敌人的部件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片危险的土地上游荡的可不只有强盗。你必须与其他移动堡垒战斗并击败它们。从他们的残骸中搜寻部件来强化自己，不然你会成为任敌人搜刮的废料！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/1c32aa3e3e175544f1603636fd03e3a2.poster.avif?t=1768382106\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/1c32aa3e3e175544f1603636fd03e3a2.webm?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/1c32aa3e3e175544f1603636fd03e3a2.mp4?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >格斗风格的空间战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换到《铁拳》2.5D格斗视图的风格，在战斗中利用侧身、闪避和冲撞。试图控制战斗空间并避开敌人的攻击时，留意可能限制行动的岩石、墙壁和其他环境特征。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/57ed723bbd38be46811e618c42b2f99b.poster.avif?t=1768382106\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/57ed723bbd38be46811e618c42b2f99b.webm?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/57ed723bbd38be46811e618c42b2f99b.mp4?t=1768382106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放慢时间的风格和策略</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用酷炫的时间放慢功能，使用武器库中的一种武器瞄准射击时，就会启动该功能。亲自控制每件武器，或者让队员随意射击，同时兼顾主动重新装弹、冷却和移动，以求在战场上发挥最高的效率。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在持久世界中吃一堑长一智</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你先前失败的旅程中，旧堡垒的残骸可能会沦落成杂草丛生的废墟，当你怀揣着对下一代的希望再次踏上征程，你可以拾取到一些部件；或者，你曾经保护过的房屋可能发展成了繁荣的村庄。  你过去的行为总会影响未来，即使是失败也是如此。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902970/extras/3c3306395d54e3058b2fdea973e497ed.avif?t=1768382106\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索城门之外的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Castle Come，你出生于高墙环绕的世界，只有一扇传说的神秘城门是通往外界的唯一途径。城门只允许每个区域最大的机甲通过。推进游戏，穿过城门，探索和收集资源，发现熔炉，最终揭开谁建造了城门以及你为何困在其中的谜团。</p>",
